version_description:
10,000 Lines of Code written.
1,250 human hours.
50 Bugs found and squashed.
10 Beta users.
1 Testers.
3 Developers
1 Goal.

The biggest update is here. It’s the app you know and love but we’ve rewritten the entire app from the ground up to make use of the best of iOS. Experience refreshed UI/UX, smoother navigation, new app name and icon, exciting new features like weight logbook, weight history charts, healthy reminder to keep you on track and much more,

We hope you love this latest update!

We'd love it if you could leave a friendly review on the App Store. Your support means a lot!
